    "Alternatively, this physiological signal can also be measured through a fully contactless approach.",
    "For instance, a proof-of-concept study in [277] proposed the feasibility of measuring electrodermal activity using a camera.Due to the necessity of hard real-time response, the processing complexity of the system is likely to increase.",
